# Incident Ticket Practice

## Ticket Number

INC-2102

---

### User

David Miller

---

### Department

Sales

---

### Reported Issue

Computer running extremely slow.

---

## Investigation

Questions asked

- When did the issue begin?
- Is every application slow?
- Did anything change recently?

Commands used

```bash
free -h
top
df -h
journalctl
```

---

## Possible Causes

- High memory usage
- High CPU usage
- Full disk
- Background process consuming resources
- Software bug

---

## Resolution

Identify root cause.

Resolve based on findings.

Examples

- Close unnecessary applications.
- Stop unnecessary processes.
- Free disk space.
- Restart affected application if appropriate.

---

## Verification

Verify

```bash
free -h
```

```bash
top
```

Confirm user can use applications normally.

---

## Ticket Documentation Format

Issue

↓

Investigation

↓

Root Cause

↓

Resolution

↓

Verification

↓

Status

