# Interview Questions

## Technical

Difference between

kill

and

kill -9

Answer:

kill sends a termination signal allowing the process to exit gracefully.

kill -9 forcefully terminates the process immediately.

---

## Scenario

A process is consuming 100% CPU.

Steps

- Identify process.
- Determine whether it is critical.
- Investigate logs.
- Resolve safely.
- Verify system performance.

